legal.confWebsiteBody:
When you use our website or contact us, we may process:
• Identity and contact details: name, email address, organisation (optional) submitted via the contact form or by email;
• Aggregated browsing data: pages viewed, device type, country — via Vercel Analytics (anonymised statistics, no advertising cookies);
• Meeting booking data: when you book a slot via the HubSpot Meetings embed on the Pro page, information entered is processed by HubSpot in accordance with their privacy policy.

legal.confAppBody:
The Vagabond mobile app may process the following categories of data:
• Account: identifier, email, username, profile photo (via Firebase Authentication);
• Location: GPS position while the app is active, to display your position, validate your presence at a place, and update your progress map;
• Activity: visited places, badges, challenges, travel statistics;
• Content: photos taken or imported during your visits;
• Preferences: public/private profile settings and notification settings.

legal.confPurposesBody:
Your data is used to:
• Provide and improve the service (map, place validation, gamification);
• Create and manage your user account;
• Respond to contact or demo requests (Vagabond Pro offer);
• Ensure security and prevent fraudulent use;
• Measure website traffic in aggregated form;
• Comply with our legal obligations.

legal.confLegalBasisBody:
We process your data on the following bases:
• Contract performance: providing the service when you use the app or request a demo;
• Legitimate interest: service improvement, security, aggregated website statistics;
• Consent: when required (e.g. mobile geolocation, push notifications) — you may withdraw consent at any time in your device or app settings.

legal.confRetentionBody:
• Contact data (website): 3 years from the last exchange;
• App account: kept while the account is active, then deleted or anonymised within 3 years of closure;
• Aggregated browsing data: according to Vercel Analytics policy.

legal.confSharingBody:
Your data may be accessible to our technical providers, solely for service needs:
• Vercel (web hosting and analytics);
• Firebase / Google Cloud (mobile authentication);
• Mapbox (mapping);
• HubSpot (B2B meeting booking);
• Fly.io and AWS (API infrastructure).
We do not sell your personal data. Transfers outside the European Union, where applicable, are governed by appropriate safeguards (standard contractual clauses or equivalent).

legal.cguAppBody:
The app is intended for personal, non-commercial use, unless otherwise agreed in writing for the Vagabond Pro offer.
It is prohibited to:
• Bypass place validation mechanisms (GPS spoofing, fake validations);
• Publish unlawful, defamatory content or content infringing third-party rights;
• Extract or massively reuse app data without authorisation;
• Disrupt the proper functioning of the service.
